'''Botswana''' ke naga lefasaneng la [[Afrika]]. ''Botswana'' e borwa ba [[Afrika]], e wela seleteng sa [[Borwa ba Afrika|Borwa Ba Afrika]].

''Botswana'' e agišane le : 
* [[Afrika Borwa]] (borwa le go ya borwa Bohlabela), 
* [[Namibia]] (bodikela),
* [[Zambia]] (leboa) le 
* [[Zimbabwe]] (leboa bohlabela).

''Botswana'' ke e tee ya dinaga tša [[Afrika]], tšeo [[landlocked|di sa bapago]] le [[lewatle]].

